{"tid":670281,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對生活冇晒激情。。。","createTime":"2018-05-19T08:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T14:31:08.000Z","uid":141543,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ae57a16786b1e195b82218054b5c45e783a461","tid":670281,"uid":141543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:27:35.000Z","msg":"腦入邊只會諗錢，但一諗錢又覺得好冇意義，但又搵唔到其他任何比錢更有意義既野。<br />\n<br />\n以前會鐘意溝下女，去下旅行，睇錶睇車，周圍去玩，但以家變到對乜都冇興趣，每日淨係留意aastock，馬會，其他搵快錢既東西。<br />\n<br />\n係社會迫到咁，抑或係自己性格問題"},{"pid":"0ff4e0df8a8ce4ea3e8147b3b03cb9b8a631c178","tid":670281,"uid":106588,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"有，每日除左返工賺錢就無咩人生目標<br />\n放假寧願留係屋企"},{"pid":"839c45e5350cb91f277ff89a8bb88bc526cd06f2","tid":670281,"uid":141543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ff4e0df8a8ce4ea3e8147b3b03cb9b8a631c178","tid":670281,"uid":106588,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"有，每日除左返工賺錢就無咩人生目標<br />\n放假寧願留係屋企"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"每日都會計自己手上有幾錢，好似心理變態咁"},{"pid":"bb02558a075fe43957554d348bf9def325352dda","tid":670281,"uid":77769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"我連錢都無諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n失戀後覺得其實自己平時既生活都幾乏味<br />\n<br />\n之前都話好想打機，而家連機都無動力開"},{"pid":"ce79954e77cca296247bcb3e6ae55785aca15f4e","tid":670281,"uid":59931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:47:03.000Z","msg":"咩都唔想做<br />\n但係唔搵工做又唔得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15027a83036ef7dd0742556a607f68124d6896c2","tid":670281,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"839c45e5350cb91f277ff89a8bb88bc526cd06f2","tid":670281,"uid":141543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ff4e0df8a8ce4ea3e8147b3b03cb9b8a631c178","tid":670281,"uid":106588,"like":3